name: Mamba Instinct 'Pure Platinum'
description: Kobe Bryant has been nicknamed the Black Mamba because of his unquestionable speed and for the passion that seeps into every single one of his games. Inspired by his agility, the Mamba Instinct 'Pure Platinum' features a Flyweave upper in a Cool Grey color scheme with Pure Platinum overlays on the tongue, side Swoosh, eyestay, laces, and toe cap. The sneaker also boasts a drop-in Lunar foam midsole for responsive cushioning and an engineered rubber outsole for superior traction.

name: Mamba Instinct 'Dark Grey'
description: In addition to its low profile and Lunarlon-cushioned midsole, the Nike Mamba Instinct is marked by a unique graphic design on its breathable Flyweave upper. The jacquard-like effect, rendered here in dark grey and white against a black backdrop, is complemented by PU threading for lightweight reinforcement. Underfoot, the thin rubber outsole is finished with a multidirectional traction pattern.

name: Mamba Instinct 'University Red'
description: Inspired by the Mambaâ€™s mentality on the court, the Kobe Mamba Instinct sneaker brings performance features together in a low, lightweight package built for speed. Released in June 2017, the University Red and black edition features a Flyweave upper atop a Lunarlon midsole.

name: Mamba Instinct 'Anthracite'
description: Part of an inaugural quartet of colorways to introduce the Nike Mamba Instinct, the Nike Mamba Instinct 'Anthracite' sneaker is an OG model that dropped in January 2017. With a mix of Anthracite and Black hues, this low-top sneaker sports a seamless Flyweave upper with a graphic jacquard print woven throughout. The shoe features a silver Swoosh on the sidewall, a Black Mamba logo on the tongue and is finished with a full-length Lunarlon sole unit.
